{"tid":1733913,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【15:34】約5、6個家長稱他們的子女在理大內，他們走到尖東橋外，要求警方讓他們手牽手進內見子女一面。","createTime":"2019-11-18T08:07:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-18T10:03:50.000Z","uid":130626,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"7049564766902ab893aee342f41caefb1374ea80","tid":1733913,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T08:07:22.000Z","msg":"【15:34】約5、6個家長稱他們的子女在理大內，他們走到尖東橋外，要求警方讓他們手牽手進內見子女一面。一名母親向警方跪地痛哭，稱「如果我個女死咗我跳樓畀你睇」；另一名家長要求見指揮官，讓他們入內，表示可以拘捕子女，不介意他們留案底，只求他們平安。有圍觀市民指罵警察，家長強調「我們只是和平，不要罵警」。<br />\n<br />\n一名女警用揚聲器稱家長挑釁人群，群眾即時表達不滿。家長現時於尖東橋口靜坐。（艾博瑜攝）<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PvJs1RV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPvJs1RV.jpg&h=9deccdc8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nSource: 明報Facebook"},{"pid":"9eba53480c7b375d418b65a08a36e7dd3e106f01","tid":1733913,"uid":49336,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T08:08:47.000Z","msg":"你的仁慈唔會換來敵人禮待<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TemFoaQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTemFoaQ.jpg&h=02bd1e1b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/str2BMv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fstr2BMv.jpg&h=de277238&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"00c47b3801987f9a89d39e8ed87fd7d3d6d2ef85","tid":1733913,"uid":233316,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9eba53480c7b375d418b65a08a36e7dd3e106f01","tid":1733913,"uid":49336,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T08:08:47.000Z","msg":"你的仁慈唔會換來敵人禮待<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TemFoaQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTemFoaQ.jpg&h=02bd1e1b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/str2BMv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fstr2BMv.jpg&h=de277238&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T08: